No one know what dot is. Just dot in desert, far away. Hugo Huckle he made a spy thing outa a glassberry, inna tube o' bone. Telly scope he called it, but we cooden see nothin'. Just as wise as they was hunned years ago. Thu dot just looked bigger. No clearer. Hugo he dead an processed now, did him no good. Eli Heffron he hev wonnerful eyes, he kin see a louse on a heep twenny step away. He say dot hev wheels like thu morgue cart. I don't b'lieve thet rubbish.
