It be a false hand fixed with big metal nails drove through middle inta wood beam in wall. Strange thing to do? Robe was hang from hand. Hand be made o' some sorta pink stuff sorta like splat fruit rind. I never seed nothin like et. There be shreds a rotted  black rag on wrist. Mebbe glove bits. I thought it were real hand first I saw et. It hev small hole in wrist look as if sumpin fit in.
> put spike in hole

> put spike in hole
Poke spike in quick. Hand go click. Odd lookin' tube fall out end o' hand. I pick et up.
> x tube

> x tube
Thu tube be shiny colour. It have a pushy thing at end. I push it. Ghost appear, float in air sittin' down. I ain't feered o' ghosts. Live folks is worse. Ghost he hev white hair an beard. He hev gold things on shoulders. He look sad, he look at me an speak but voice come from thu tube.

"My name is Jules Kaminski. Captain of the I.P.S. Starship 'Aries'.  I hope that this will never be played. If you are watching this holcast the chances are that we will all be dead.

We are the crew of the 'Aries'.  Eight men, seven women. We set down on Dracos 4 yesterday on the fourth of April 2426. The planet seems to be almost total desert, although there seem to be small pockets of life mainly in meteor craters. We left the ship in auto sentinel mode. Young Henry Bayliss set the password. The name of his beloved again I suppose. We set out to survey a likely crater in the ATV. Unfortunately a separated input pipe released all our induction fluid into the sand. The pipe was easily fixed but the loss of just two litres of fluid has reduced a twenty-seater ATV. to so much inert metal. The ship is impossibly far off on foot with the  limited air we have at present. The Oxy Unit is not operational with the complete power failure we have suffered. How such a catastrophic malfunction is possible beats me. I can only suspect sabotage, but by whom?"

Here the ghost shrug shoulders and hold out hands show palms. Ghost fade out then reappear. Ghost speak strange, use some words I don' unnerstan'.

"We have taken refuge in the large meteor crater. After a trek from the ATV using almost all the oxy in our personal breather units. There is no hope of replenishing them. There seems to be ample oxy here released by a huge tree covering almost all of the crater. Animals and plants of several kinds live under it providing us with a rather bland diet. We are prisoners here, made worse by the fact that we can still see the ATV as a faint dot in the desert. André du Pont  believes he can replicate the lost induction fluid using local fruit juice mixed with various chemicals he carries in his survey kit. Unfortunately his supply is limited and only one batch is possible."

Ghost fade then he come back. He look ill (if ghost can look ill?)

"Du Pont has failed, we are doomed. He successfully produced the fluid using the last of his chemicals. He insisted on making the trip to the ATV himself using the last working breather. Halfway we saw him fall. He did not rise, we could only watch him die of asphyxiation while the distant useless ATV mocked us. The man was a hero.

I fear for the crews' sanity, the lack of civilisation, the bland diet and apathy are already causing forgetfulness and a loss of proper human behaviour. I have a small supply of Vit capsules that will soon run out to keep me sane and help me maintain some  form of discipline as long as possible.  Oh for an Updater Unit to fix the brain drain, the nearest is in the vehicle. The Colt eight point has disappeared. I suspect Lieutenant Teasdale. He is plotting something with Sally Hopkins. They have made a small replica of the Aries from two dish shaped fruit rinds and some small sticks. They parade it about on a pole marching it round the tree, singing and chanting. Strangely they seem to be gaining some support for their odd behaviour. I feel that my time as Captain has almost come. I am hiding this recording where I hope they won't find it. But I can't even be sure of that.
Farewell!"

Ghost he lift flat right hand to head then snap back to side, then click heels. Right hand have black glove like Stingbush cutter wear, left not have glove. He fade and not come back.

I unnerstand bits a this, some I don't. Thu ghost he hev funny ways o' talkin'. I think I unnerstand enough to know what happen. People hev kids an they  be us I reckons. Mebbe I should keep tube safe.
